    "text": "21st Century NICS Act\n\nThis bill modifies procedures for conducting firearms-related background checks through the national instant criminal background check system (NICS).\n\nSpecifically, it permits the NICS to query an additional database\u2014the National Data Exchange\u2014as part of a firearm-related background check."
  },
